{"tid":1727583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發】政府稱駐港解放軍協助清理路障屬自發非政府請求","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T02:53:18.000Z","uid":97944,"like":97,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"b3de71f7d0101397438a52ea040954e90586c598","tid":1727583,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"一批身穿便服的駐港解放軍下午步出九龍塘九龍東軍營，清理路障。政府發言人回覆表示，駐軍協助清理路障，純屬駐軍自發義務性質，並非特區政府請求協助。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍駐香港部隊新聞發言人則表示，駐軍部分官兵是加入在軍營附近聯福道的市民，配合清理軍營門口道路。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492649-20191116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492649-20191116.htm&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=821c9e4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492649-20191116.htm&h=53fa99b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492649-20191116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a31ede8d2b3ab044f47e41002cbcc21091503bf1","tid":1727583,"uid":181474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"其實出解放軍係國際核彈嘅另一論調<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ebceb6d8b7ce6d2f865abb3d4960600368e7638","tid":1727583,"uid":238046,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"駐軍法點寫？"},{"pid":"aa19af23714ff6c118900a47112f3891023a417a","tid":1727583,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dae9f3ce7149083f3e1ca5a0570edabd8742fd1","tid":1727583,"uid":121146,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"一國兩制正式完結"},{"pid":"fa8400232ea63ee81342485c96879aaa0db545db","tid":1727583,"uid":134744,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"reply